**************************************INFO******************************************************

Simple game in C language basen on allegro 5 library.

You must destroy as many enemies as you can. :)
Game ends when you die.

Id you wan't to change settings, you should modify "game.conf" file.

Author : KAMIL PIOTROWSKI

Ship graphics: 	MillionthVector (Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License)
			https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

************************************COMPILE***************************************************
RUN: ./compile.sh 	(required allegro 5 library)
*************************************PLAY*****************************************************
RUN: ./game.play
